<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4598917>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. — Representative leaf shapes from humid and littoral forest species of Scolopia Schreb.:A, S. hazomby (Razakamalala et al. 3507); B, S.thouvenotii (Schatz 2741); C, S. taimbarina (Antilahimena et al. 4309); D, S. montana (Randrianaivo et al. 608); E, S. manongarivae (Miller & Randrianasolo 4475); F, S. manongarivae of high elevation (Birkinshaw 885); G, S. erythrocarpa (Rabevohitra et al. 4800); H, S. orientalis (Ludovic 746); I, S. madagascariensis (Razakamalala et al. 160); J, S. delphinensis, sp. nov. (Ramison 475)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4598917/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

